Product Description

Never Ordinary

Standout in sustainable fashion with uppercaseIndias 1st GRS-certified bags brand. We are an environmentally sensitive brand of Travel Gear for the young with a taste for things that dont just help them look or feel good but also do good. And it's ready to get working and go places with you.

Features that Stand Out!

Stylish and sturdy yet lightweight, the uppercase day backpack is made with premium quality robust material with sturdy stitching, it offers a little extra than what you need for your school essentials.

Designed with Care

This 19L anti-theft laptop backpack promises durability, robustness, and reliability. It successfully goes through the tear test, break test, and 2000 jolt test before it reaches you.

Strength & Safety

This durable bag features a smooth inner surface and a wrinkle-free, sturdy outer that stays upright.

Storage & Organisation

Designed for your convenience, this bag has a front zipper pocket, a side bottle pocket, and a tablet sleeve for better organization.

Anti-Theft Laptop Compartment

It is designed with a 15.6" laptop compartment and comfortable air mesh padding to keep you going.

Designed for good - A Promise of Sustainable and Ethical Production Choose uppercase for sustainable bags that don't compromise on quality. Our school backpack is made with premium recycled material and is GRS-certified for sustainability, making it a stylish step towards sustainability.

How are ratings calculated?

 Was looking for a medium size bag which can carry my laptop as well as daily essentials. Came across this bag and liked that the material used can be recycled.

Was bit skeptical to order since it was a new product , but since Amazon gives a return window , went ahead with it.

The bag was delivered within 4 days of placing the order , came nicely packed .

And glad that ordered this one

1. The size is perfect and looks trendy , the black color is perfect
2. Is trolley compatible , which is a big plus since I travel regularly
3. The main compartment has an internal organizer , which allows to keep all things nicely

5. The zippers are smooth and look durable and the outer flap gives it a premium look. Also has a bottle holder
